<h3 id="about">About</h3>
<p><br /></p>

<p>I’m a machine learning researcher with more than 15 years of experience in the broader field. I completed my EngD under the supervision of Professors <a href="http://www0.cs.ucl.ac.uk/staff/J.Shawe-Taylor/" target="blank"><strong>John Shawe-Taylor</strong></a> and Delmiro Fernandez-Reyes and I’ve published in the domains of computational biology, medicine, and privacy-preserving machine learning. My professional experience spans a number of settings including security, biotechnology, and finance. You might find some of my <a href="#/features/02-publications"><strong>research</strong></a> interesting,  or perhaps you’d like to have a look at my CV.</p>

